# Org-control / Project context

This project (**{{PROJECT_NAME}}**) uses org-control (org skills only; no MCP required). Org preferences (strictness, ask_before) are used by org skills; use **org-preferences** to read or update them.

**Stack / context:** {{STACK_SUMMARY}}

**Conventions:** {{CONVENTIONS_SUMMARY}}

- When planning or enforcing policy, use **org-orchestrator** and **org-preferences**.
